summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 70W, page 167 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Dumar's Highland Park Addition, Lots 9 to 14 incl., Block E, located on the east side of 9th Ave. S.W., north of West Holden St., as Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone.
